  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Mantras are specialized energized sound or words, which are defined most important sound
      therapy in Vedic healing. Present study was undertaken to evaluate the immediate effect of
      specialized Mantra chant on cardiovascular parameters in high blood pressure patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
